liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Fridolina Rolfo drills her left-footed strike low and to her right. Mackenzie Arnold dives the right way and sticks her left mitt out, getting within centimetres of it, but the ball finds the bottom corner. Sweden lead 1-0 after half an hour.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: SWEDEN HITS THE FRONT!!

children.content: Fridolina Rolfo drills her left-footed strike low and to her right. Mackenzie Arnold dives the right way and sticks her left mitt out, getting within centimetres of it, but the ball finds the bottom corner.
So close to another Mackenzie Arnold MOMENT.
Sweden lead 1-0 after half an hour.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Replays show Clare Hunt clearly clipped the foot of Stina Blackstenius as they ursued the ball down the right side of the box, and the referee sends Sweden to the spot. Fridolina Rolfo will take the shot. Does Mackenzie Arnold have another miracle penalty save in her?
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: PENALTY SWEDEN

children.content: Replays show Clare Hunt clearly clipped the foot of Stina Blackstenius as they ursued the ball down the right side of the box, and the referee sends Sweden to the spot.

liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: Clare Hunt gets tangled up with Stina Blackstenius and they both go down. Sweden almost scores on the advantage, but Fridolina Rolfo's header hits the crossbar. But the referee is checking for a penalty with VAR.
liveBlogPostPrepared.title: 26' SWEDEN HIT THE WOODWORK! But we may have a penalty here
